data.description: Barely lived in and ready for move-in!  This home offers 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths with the master bedroom downstairs, plus a media/game room upstairs!  As you walk in the front door you are greeted by the front entry that leads into the living room which opens to the kitchen and dining area.  The backyard is already set up ready to entertain and enjoy the built in fire pit.  The other 3 bedrooms are upstairs with the spacious media room perfect for movie night!
